text: Rogelio Martínez may refer to: * Rogelio Martínez (baseball) (1918–2010), Cuban baseball pitcher in Major League Baseball * Rogelio Martínez (boxer) (born 1974), Dominican Republic boxer * Rogelio Martínez Díaz, Afro-Cuban musician with Sonora Matancera * Rogelio Nores Martínez (1906–1975), Argentine engineer and politician
title: Rogelio Martínez
